{"about_the_game":"MythBusters: The Game is an official video game adaptation of the legendary Discovery show. Become a Mythbuster yourself, both in front of and behind the camera!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/811550/extras/mew001.gif?t=1730368148\" /><br><br>Utilize the full MythBusters Workshop, and explore other locations like the warehouse, MythBusters Hall, and the testing ground. There\u2019s always a new myth to unlock, so level up to try the next experiment. Be careful and be prepared, because each experiment carries a huge risk. And remember: don't try it at home!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/811550/extras/new006.gif?t=1730368148\" /><br><br>In MythBusters: The Game, you can:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Solve puzzles in the Blueprint Zone to work out the mechanics of each myth<br></li><li>Collect the materials for experiments and craft the equipment to use<br></li><li>Bring the experiment to life by setting it up and testing it out<br></li><li>Confirm or bust crazy real-life myths, or deem them plausible<br></li><li>Build your audience to get as much popularity as you can!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/811550/extras/new003a.gif?t=1730368148\" /><br><br>Fund and cut your episodes to grow the popularity of the show! First, manage your production budget and inventory. Once you conduct your experiments, play with the video editing module wisely, choosing the best bits to show. Make sure you have everything you need to impress the audience!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Stunt Staple","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/811550/d175a4a5b50f89afe5fb381d59c34e929aaf96c2.jpg"},{"name":"Bullet Bender","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/811550/2e4cbe03a3036d